22508250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/9dc0a4e0e8ffaead1f4907c4a796a1cb.avif?t=1722508250\" width=512 height=128 /></span><br>Organize your items on shelves and set their prices. Products without a market value can be evaluated at an appraiser/evaluator.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/cd4a2157f43cd332ffffdc8056987b16.poster.avif?t=1722508250\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/cd4a2157f43cd332ffffdc8056987b16.webm?t=1722508250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/cd4a2157f43cd332ffffdc8056987b16.mp4?t=1722508250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/417fff29c77d92819fe91e16e5caab5c.avif?t=1722508250\" width=512 height=128 /></span><br>Move to checkout and become a cashier, process the items and payment, exactly like in a supermarket. <br>You can sell or buy items from clients.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/81a28d89bd8b72d9695771ac46fbfdce.poster.avif?t=1722508250\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/81a28d89bd8b72d9695771ac46fbfdce.webm?t=1722508250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036140/extras/81a28d89bd8b72d9695771ac46fbfdce.mp4?t=1722508250\" type=\"